parameters: I will give you all this, if you kneel
Go away, Satan! The scripture says:
Worship the Lord your God and serve only him!
Yo te dar todo esto, si te arrodillas
Vete, Satans, porque la Escritura dice:
Adora al Seor tu Dios y srvele solo a l.
Et donar tot aix si et prosternes i m'adores.
Senyor, el teu Du, dna culte a ell tot sol."
\C[18]After this, Jesus went back on his way
\C[18]Despus de esto, Jess retom su camino
el seu cam cap al nord de Jeric.
\I[128]It hasn't hurt you, you are protected
\I[128]No te ha hecho dao, ests protegido
